{"tid":2123043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明行動 兩女生涉堵路兼搜出食用油 守行為兩年","createTime":"2020-07-24T11:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T11:16:29.000Z","uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"60692d08233aa1478f7b1e59a05e7033ed2d60f0","tid":2123043,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:04:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">黎明行動 兩女生涉堵路兼搜出食用油 守行為兩年</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）去年11月11日，有網民發起「黎明行動」在多區主要幹道進行堵路。兩名女學生被控一項在公眾地方造成阻礙罪，今日（23日）於九龍城裁判法院提堂。控方同意以簽保守行為方式處理案件，兩人獲准自簽2,000元和守行為24個月，控罪獲撤回。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075796?fbclid=IwAR28exnwCw4jVbCJox299-huyBd0TFDl8l9Y3IZNPutJTynqySx1WV_ZPSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075796%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR28exnwCw4jVbCJox299-huyBd0TFDl8l9Y3IZNPutJTynqySx1WV_ZPSM&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=848440e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075796%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR28exnwCw4jVbCJox299-huyBd0TFDl8l9Y3IZNPutJTynqySx1WV_ZPSM&h=fe6f1825\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075796?fbclid=IwAR28exnwCw4jVbCJox299-huyBd0TFDl8l9Y3IZNPutJTynqySx1WV_ZPSM</a>"},{"pid":"04e8ee80b9d8c656772a1fb9b5dfe90e9623cfe6","tid":2123043,"uid":118553,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"食用油都要告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b16414ac37e5275fe319dfae71abce8241266a","tid":2123043,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:05:50.000Z","msg":"食用油 六角匙都可以入獄 厲害了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f4eeac3d14411704db488e3299851d76b69305","tid":2123043,"uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"幫阿媽落街買食用油煮飯唔得?<br />\n<br />\n既然食用油係危險物品 不如告埋惠康百佳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2kCxED.jpg\" 